{"tid":1626380,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"關於攪Starbucks, 元気, 吉野家等專營權企業","createTime":"2019-10-05T10:58:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T13:40:10.000Z","uid":5216,"like":229,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":65,"replies":[{"pid":"fa80bfcce98a9a8a16ef85ab11cc23be11d1e81d","tid":1626380,"uid":5216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:58:12.000Z","msg":"我聽咗劉細良個節目，佢講咗一樣嘢可以參考吓。就係我哋未必一定吓吓幫佢裝修，反而應該繼續罷食、喺佢門口派傳單叫人唔好食，再收工之後幫佢貼文宣同噴漆文宣。<br />\n<br />\n同時，寫信去佢外國總公司，講晒佢哋嘅罪行，點樣得罪香港人，要求佢哋收回專營權。依個方法之前都有手足用喺党鐵喺外國嘅經營業務上面。同時可以用喺所有得罪過香港人嘅專營權企業度。<br />\n<br />\n話晒喺香洪嘅最代理得罪我哋，本身間外資係無辜嘅。所最好嘅方法係令香港嘅奶共撐警代理仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家覺得有冇得諗呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0c2MaPkO-Hw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0c2MaPkO-Hw&d=YADvn44w83N9IBOkVydrk4TtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=8ab9dc05\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0c2MaPkO-Hw</a><br />\n<br />\n有興趣可由47:50開始聽"},{"pid":"bb97ec22aadd41e4fdf107b04c5d77a6915f1a87","tid":1626380,"uid":5216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:58:47.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n槍仇必報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n612 721 811 831 929 101 新屋嶺 第二槍 緊急法 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd2630d864e720ced66d0d4ea4050ddd169a3858","tid":1626380,"uid":270629,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:59:21.000Z","msg":"香港人俾政府恰到上心口！<br />\n「反蒙面法」都用緊急法立埋<br />\n如果你連三罷公投都唔表態<br />\n你 註定輸一世！<br />\n<br />\n公投截止日期：10月11日中午12點<br />\n<br />\nTh